{"tid":401000,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過無啦啦突然昏迷左","createTime":"2017-09-15T09:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T09:59:28.000Z","uid":126736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"50aef6026def66eb425f6e8fe415df7ef92f21fa","tid":401000,"uid":126736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T09:26:14.000Z","msg":"一世人試過兩次 今年25 歲<br />\n一次19 歲 一次24 歲<br />\n<br />\n第一次係係lecture room <br />\nBreak 果陣起身諗住去廁所 起身行左幾步覺得好唔舒服就暈低左 起返身已經落左堂係輪椅上面有幾個老師係隔離 前後10 分鐘左右<br />\n<br />\n第二次係係屋企廁所 今次冇人係隔離 沖完涼身都未抹乾忽然間覺得好唔舒服就暈左 起身係浴缸邊仲要成身撞到瘀哂但唔知點撞 前後我諗都係一兩個字左右<br />\n<br />\n兩次都毫無預兆<br />\n但年年都做body check 又話冇事<br />\n有冇人都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c17681d089f9a78b8ced2f0ce4d6fc56c8935a","tid":401000,"uid":105011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T09:27:32.000Z","msg":"搵龍哥睇下好喎"},{"pid":"f79e24a7d1f7e30f2c87a9dd9940afbab8149a0b","tid":401000,"uid":136924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T09:27:55.000Z","msg":"正正常常冇捱夜？"},{"pid":"22722dbbe9a1f7810579fc4a8d46e1ec3928c7d7","tid":401000,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T09:33:22.000Z","msg":"check真d好 講埋俾醫生知試過無啦啦暈"},{"pid":"84c52b973e7a9e6aaf4a8a3a65dda1474348382c","tid":401000,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T09:46:30.000Z","msg":"睇下醫生好喎"},{"pid":"63ebb66a8eaadc67632f79c91274ac14a582b302","tid":401000,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T09:46:59.000Z","msg":"耳水不平衡"},{"pid":"29b21439b367f1b97850eb93658c18135b0d228a","tid":401000,"uid":29441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T09:59:28.000Z","msg":"認真 我姑姐之前無啦啦暈左<br />\n之後送返醫院發現腦中風之後腦幹死亡<br />\n救唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}